  ('medical-tech-moex-17788', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-096-05118730', 'sub-medical-tech-09', NULL, 'single_choice', '血液培養瓶中所含之 sodium polyanethol sulfonate 會抑制一些細菌（比如：Peptostreptococcus anaerobius）之生長，可添加下列何種成分於培養基，以中和此抑制作用？', '["resin", "agar", "gelatin", "sodium thioglycollate"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c1b8543e6e72", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0579d7726f66", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096040", "c": "105", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學及臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫、心理、呼吸治療、營養師、獸醫人員考試暨醫師分試考試第一試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-17789', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-096-05118730', 'sub-medical-tech-09', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於院內感染（nosocomial infection）的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["只要嚴格遵守相關的感染控制規定，院內感染是可以完全避免的", "泌尿道感染通常不屬於院內感染", "院內感染可能是病人內因性（endogenous）細菌造成的感染", "只要同一個病房的二名病人在一週內都分離出相同生物型（biotype）的病原菌，即確定有院內感 染之群突發（outbreak）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c1b8543e6e72", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0579d7726f66", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096040", "c": "105", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學及臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫、心理、呼吸治療、營養師、獸醫人員考試暨醫師分試考試第一試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-17790', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-096-05118730', 'sub-medical-tech-09', NULL, 'single_choice', '用disk diffusion及dilution susceptibility test方法測得Streptococcus pneumoniae 對penicillin具抗藥 性，則此菌株抗penicillin之機轉最可能為：', '["PBP gene mutation", "細胞壁阻擋penicillin通過", "內生性抗藥性（intrinsic resistance）", "質體基因產物使菌體加速排除藥物"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c1b8543e6e72", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0579d7726f66", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096040", "c": "105", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學及臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫、心理、呼吸治療、營養師、獸醫人員考試暨醫師分試考試第一試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-17791', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-096-05118730', 'sub-medical-tech-09', NULL, 'single_choice', '若一菌株對某抗生素的藥敏試驗結果，原本應為感受性，卻誤判為抗藥性，通常稱之為？', '["very minor error", "minor error", "major error", "very major error"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c1b8543e6e72", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0579d7726f66", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096040", "c": "105", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學及臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫、心理、呼吸治療、營養師、獸醫人員考試暨醫師分試考試第一試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-17792', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-096-05118730', 'sub-medical-tech-09', NULL, 'single_choice', '急性細菌性腦膜炎通常會造成腦脊髓液（CSF）之何種變化？', '["蛋白質上升，葡萄糖下降，嗜中性白血球增多", "蛋白質與葡萄糖均上升，嗜中性白血球減少", "蛋白質下降，葡萄糖上升，單核白血球增多", "蛋白質與葡萄糖均下降，單核白血球減少"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c1b8543e6e72", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0579d7726f66", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096040", "c": "105", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學及臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫、心理、呼吸治療、營養師、獸醫人員考試暨醫師分試考試第一試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-17793', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-096-05118730', 'sub-medical-tech-09', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於Extended-spectrum β-lactamases（ESBL）之敘述，何者正確？', '["此酵素之基因通常位於質體，較常見於Klebsiella pneumoniae、Escherichia coli等腸內菌", "對carbapenems通常呈抗性", "屬於Ambler Class C β-lactamase", "酵素活性位含lysine，與β-lactam水解作用有直接關係"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c1b8543e6e72", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0579d7726f66", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096040", "c": "105", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學及臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫、心理、呼吸治療、營養師、獸醫人員考試暨醫師分試考試第一試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
